Simple decorators (usable in Python >= 2.4).

Example:

```
@synchronized(thread.allocate_lock())
def f():
    "Synchronized function"
    print("i am synchronized:", f, f.__doc__)

@deprecated
def g():
    "this function is deprecated"
    pass

@notimplemented
def h():
    "todo"
    pass
```

